                    <span>A few discrepancies between the examples, explanations, and especially the CD, eg: where I think she changed a file or variable name in one place and forgot to change it in the other, so you spend some time trying to reconstruct what she meant to say.<br>Otherwise well paced, good for learning.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Inheritance</div>
